<section id="about" class="py-20 lg:py-32 relative overflow-hidden section-transition">
  <!-- Background Effects -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-gray-900 via-gray-800 to-gray-900"></div>
  <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-cyan-400 to-transparent opacity-50"></div>

  <div class="relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <!-- Storytelling Section -->
    <div class="text-center mb-20">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-500/20 to-purple-500/20 border border-cyan-500/30 rounded-full text-cyan-300 mb-8">
        <span class="text-lg">✨</span>
        <span class="font-semibold">NOTRE HISTOIRE</span>
      </div>
      
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold mb-8">
        <span class="neon-text-pink">{{ section.settings.title_line_1 | default: "L'Art Du" }}</span>
        <br />
        <span class="text-white">{{ section.settings.title_line_2 | default: "Néon" }}</span>
      </h2>
      
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto space-y-6 text-lg text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
        <p>
          🎨 <strong class="text-cyan-400">Il y a 10 ans</strong>, nous avons commencé avec une vision simple : 
          <span class="text-yellow-400">transformer chaque espace en une œuvre d'art lumineuse</span>. 
          Aujourd'hui, plus de <strong class="text-green-400">500 créations</strong> illuminent la France.
        </p>
        <p>
          💡 De la <strong>petite boutique parisienne</strong> au <strong>restaurant étoilé</strong>, 
          du <strong>mariage de rêve</strong> à l'<strong>enseigne corporate</strong>, 
          chaque projet porte notre signature : <span class="text-purple-400">l'excellence artisanale française</span>.
        </p>
        <p>
          🏆 <strong class="text-pink-400">98% de nos clients</strong> nous recommandent parce que nous ne créons pas 
          juste des néons, nous <span class="neon-text-cyan">donnons vie à vos émotions</span>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Avantages Section -->
    <div class="cosmic-noise bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-800/50 to-gray-900/50 rounded-3xl p-8 lg:p-12 border border-gray-700 mb-20 relative overflow-hidden">
      <!-- Animated Border -->
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-500/20 via-purple-500/20 to-pink-500/20 rounded-3xl blur-xl opacity-50 animate-pulse"></div>
      
      <div class="relative z-10">
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
          <h3 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">
            <span class="neon-text-pink">🎯 Pourquoi Choisir LumiNéon ?</span>
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg">
            Les avantages qui font la différence
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <div class="text-center group relative">
            <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-r from-green-500 to-emerald-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 group-hover:scale-125 group-hover:rotate-12 transition-all duration-500 shadow-lg shadow-green-500/30">
              <span class="text-2xl">🇫🇷</span>
              <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-green-400/20 rounded-full scale-0 group-hover:scale-150 transition-transform duration-500 blur-md"></div>
            </div>
            <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3 group-hover:text-green-400 transition-colors duration-300">Made in France</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">Fabrication 100% française avec savoir-faire artisanal transmis de génération en génération.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="text-center group relative">
            <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-cyan-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 group-hover:scale-125 group-hover:rotate-12 transition-all duration-500 shadow-lg shadow-blue-500/30">
              <span class="text-2xl">⚡</span>
              <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-blue-400/20 rounded-full scale-0 group-hover:scale-150 transition-transform duration-500 blur-md"></div>
            </div>
            <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3 group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors duration-300">Livraison Express</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">Production 7-12 jours + livraison 2-3 jours partout en France avec suivi temps réel.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="text-center group relative">
            <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-500 to-pink-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 group-hover:scale-125 group-hover:rotate-12 transition-all duration-500 shadow-lg shadow-purple-500/30">
              <span class="text-2xl">🛡️</span>
              <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-purple-400/20 rounded-full scale-0 group-hover:scale-150 transition-transform duration-500 blur-md"></div>
            </div>
            <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3 group-hover:text-purple-400 transition-colors duration-300">Garantie Premium</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">2 ans de garantie pièces et main d'œuvre + support technique 24/7 inclus.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="text-center group relative">
            <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-500 to-orange-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 group-hover:scale-125 group-hover:rotate-12 transition-all duration-500 shadow-lg shadow-yellow-500/30">
              <span class="text-2xl">🎨</span>
              <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-yellow-400/20 rounded-full scale-0 group-hover:scale-150 transition-transform duration-500 blur-md"></div>
            </div>
            <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3 group-hover:text-yellow-400 transition-colors duration-300">Design Sur Mesure</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">Chaque création est unique, pensée spécialement pour votre projet et votre identité.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="text-center group relative">
            <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-r from-red-500 to-pink-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 group-hover:scale-125 group-hover:rotate-12 transition-all duration-500 shadow-lg shadow-red-500/30">
              <span class="text-2xl">💎</span>
              <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-red-400/20 rounded-full scale-0 group-hover:scale-150 transition-transform duration-500 blur-md"></div>
            </div>
            <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3 group-hover:text-red-400 transition-colors duration-300">Qualité Premium</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">LED Samsung dernière génération, matériaux nobles et finitions irréprochables.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="text-center group relative">
            <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-500 to-purple-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 group-hover:scale-125 group-hover:rotate-12 transition-all duration-500 shadow-lg shadow-indigo-500/30">
